        "text_tXHV4n": {
          "type": "text",
          "name": "t:names.text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>At Krini, our craftsmanship travels far and wide. Headquartered in India, we proudly collaborate with architects, designers, and developers across the country — from modern city homes to large-scale real estate projects.<br/><br/>Through our export partnerships in the USA, Middle East, and other global destinations, we bring Indian artistry and innovation to the world stage. Each piece we craft reflects our promise of quality, precision, and timeless design, delivered seamlessly across borders.<br/><br/>Whether it’s a bespoke furniture order for a boutique apartment in Mumbai or a hospitality fit-out in Texas — Krini’s global logistics network ensures that design knows no boundaries.</p>",
